name: cubed vortex
description: Created with vintage paint software from 1990-91 : Ultrapaint for Macintosh Plus and Deluxe paint IV for Commodore Amiga. This work also speaks to the history of paint software for early personal computers, and how the processes associated with this history are being incorporated into the current monetization of digital art.  ::artwork info:: 1920x1080, 30 fps. 2020/2021.
